-)Service Builder
Service builder is a code generation Tool in liferay That reads the Service.xml file and auto
Generates the BoilerPlate code for Model ,Local Service ,Remote Service ,Persistance and more .

-)service.xml
# service.xml is a confriguation file in service builder
#it is a powerfull code generation tool
# through XML we define Entities and their Attributes and how they Relate to Each other .

-)From where can you increase the database column size in Service Builder?
from portlet-model-hints.xml file

